===Noun===
# (''Greek mythology'') A [[king]] who sought and was for a while granted the cherished but subtly dangerous [[magic]]al [[power]] to turn anything he [[touch]]ed into [[gold]].
# By extension, metaphorically, used to refer to any situation in which a seeming [[virtue]] carries a terrible, hidden [[cost]].

